n Olmsted County, Minnesota. <em>Gastroenterology</em> 1997;112(5):1448–1456.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/S0016-5085(97)70025-8">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9136821/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Prevalence+and+clinical+spectrum+of+gastroesophageal+reflux%3A+a+population-based+study+in+Olmsted+County%2C+Minnesota&amp;author=GR+Locke&amp;author=NJ+Talley&amp;author=SL+Fett&amp;author=AR+Zinsmeister&amp;author=LJ+Melton&amp;publication_year=1997&amp;journal=Gastroenterology&amp;pages=1448-1456&amp;doi=10.1016%2FS0016-5085%2897%2970025-8&amp;pmid=9136821">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">7.</div><div id="r7" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Marik PE, Kaplan D. Aspiration pneumonia and dysphagia in the elderly. <em>Chest</em> 2003;124(1):328–336.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1378/chest.124.1.328">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12853541/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Aspiration+pneumonia+and+dysphagia+in+the+elderly&amp;author=PE+Marik&amp;author=D+Kaplan&amp;publication_year=2003&amp;journal=Chest&amp;pages=328-336&amp;doi=10.1378%2Fchest.124.1.328&amp;pmid=12853541">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">8.</div><div id="r8" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Cook IJ. Oropharyngeal dysphagia. <em>Gastroenterol Clin North Am</em> 2009;38(3):411–431.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.gtc.2009.06.003">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19699405/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Oropharyngeal+dysphagia&amp;author=IJ+Cook&amp;publication_year=2009&amp;journal=Gastroenterol+Clin+North+Am&amp;pages=411-431&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.gtc.2009.06.003&amp;pmid=19699405">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">9.</div><div id="r9" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Schindler JS, Kelly JH. Swallowing disorders in the elderly. <em>Laryngoscope</em> 2002;112(4):589–602.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1097/00005537-200204000-00001">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12150508/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Swallowing+disorders+in+the+elderly&amp;author=JS+Schindler&amp;author=JH+Kelly&amp;publication_year=2002&amp;journal=Laryngoscope&amp;pages=589-602&amp;doi=10.1097%2F00005537-200204000-00001&amp;pmid=12150508">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">10.</div><div id="r10" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Levine MS, Rubesin SE. Radiologic investigation of dysphagia. <em>AJR Am J Roentgenol</em> 1990;154(6):1157–1163.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.2214/ajr.154.6.2110721">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/2110721/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Radiologic+investigation+of+dysphagia&amp;author=MS+Levine&amp;author=SE+Rubesin&amp;publication_