580"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ijsu.2017.08.580">Long-term outcome of laparoscopic Nissen fundoplication in a regional hospital setting</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Dimitrios Prassas</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Andreas Krieg</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Thomas-Marten Rolfs</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Franz-Josef Schumacher</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2017Oct1 | International Journal of Surgery, Vol. 46</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ijsu.2017.08.580">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1590/s1806-37562016000000273"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1590/s1806-37562016000000273">Chest CT findings in patients with dysphagia and aspiration: a systematic review</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Betina Scheeren</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Erissandra Gomes</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Giordano Alves</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Edson Marchiori</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Bruno Hochhegger</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">1 August 2017 | Jornal Brasileiro de Pneumologia, Vol. 43, No. 4</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1590/s1806-37562016000000273">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.53347/rID-52850"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" 